.dantri.com.vn/2022/09/21/hyundai-i10-facelift-scoop-3-1663721512956.jpg\" data-photo-id=\"2143343\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-image\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-image_2143343\" data-content-target=\"/o-to-xe-may/bat-gap-hyundai-i10-mau-moi-tren-duong-thu-co-chi-tiet-gay-to-mo-20220921090018802.htm\" data-src=\"https://icdn.dantri.com.vn/thumb_w/680/2022/09/21/hyundai-i10-facelift-scoop-3-1663721512956.jpg\"></figure> <figure class=\"image align-center\" contenteditable=\"false\"><img title=\"Bắt gặp Hyundai i10 mẫu mới trên đường thử, có chi tiết gây tò mò - 8\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D'http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg'%20viewBox%3D'0%200%201920%201280'%2F%3E\" alt=\"Bắt gặp Hyundai i10 mẫu mới trên đường thử, có chi tiết gây tò mò - 8\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1280\" data-original=\"https://icdn.dantri.com.vn/2022/09/21/hyundai-i10-facelift-scoop-1-1663721512872.jpg\" data-photo-id=\"2143342\" data-track-content=\"\" data-content-name=\"article-content-image\" data-content-piece=\"article-content-image_2143342\" data-content-target=\"/o-to-xe-may/bat-gap-hyundai-i10-mau-moi-tren-duong-thu-co-chi-tiet-gay-to-mo-20220921090018802.htm\" data-src=\"https://icdn.dantri.com.vn/thumb_w/680/2022/09/21/hyundai-i10-facelift-scoop-1-1663721512872.jpg\"></figure> <p style=\"text-align:right\">Ảnh: <em>Carscoops</em></p> </div>"}